data.description: Your safe space is waiting for you in Atlanta! Discover the tranquility of this well-appointed condo, boasting EXTRA LOFT SPACE for versatility. Nestled in the heart of Atlantic Station, this residence not only offers seamless living but also presents a myriad of benefits for the discerning buyer. With a prime location, you'll enjoy easy access to a vibrant city life, exquisite dining options, and a thriving work scene. The well-designed layout and modern amenities of this condo ensure comfort and convenience, creating an ideal retreat that effortlessly caters to your lifestyle. Schedule a tour today and immerse yourself in the unique charm and practical advantages that this city dwelling has to offer. Rent to own option available.
